</div>
<div class="text-sm text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400 truncate pr-2">Become large enough for a garment.</div>
<div class="text-sm text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400 italic truncate pr-2">"The kid will grow into that coat."</div>
<div class="flex flex-wrap gap-1.5">
