<span class="text-xs font-medium text-yellow-700 dark:text-yellow-400">Learning</span>
</span>
</div>
<div class="text-xs text-gray-400">Oct 24, 2023</div>
<div class="flex justify-end opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity">
