</div>
</div>
<div class="text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 truncate pr-2">(of a voice or words) sweet or musical; pleasant to hear.</div>
<div class="text-sm text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400 italic truncate pr-2">"She had a rich, mellifluous voice."</div>
<div class="flex flex-wrap gap-1.5">
<span class="px-2 py-0.5 rounded bg-purple-100 dark:bg-purple-900/30 text-purple-700 dark:text-purple-300 text-xs font-medium border border-purple-200 dark:border-purple-800">Adjective</span>
<span class="px-2 py-0.5 rounded bg-orange-100 dark:bg-orange-900/30 text-orange-700 dark:text-orange-300 text-xs font-medium border border-orange-200 dark:border-orange-800">Advanced</span>
</div>
